                <span class="title">Why we collect your personal information:</span>
                <ol>
                    <li>Because it helps us to deliver a superior level of customer service. It enables
                        us to give you convenient access to our products and services and focus on categories
                        of greatest interest to you. </li>
                    <li>In addition, your personal information helps us to keep you posted on the latest
                        product and service announcements, updates, special offers, and events that you
                        might like to hear about.</li>
                    <p>
                        The Expressshow! website(www.expressshow.com), allows you to create an Expressshow!
                        registered Mobile number based on your personal information. This convenient service
                        saves you time and allows for easier use of our web services.
                    </p>
                </ol>
                <span class="title">How it Works:</span>
                <ol>
                    <li>You create a personal profile providing only your Phone Number and choose a password
                        for security. </li>
                    <li>The system saves your information and assigns you a personal Expressshow! account
                        with registered Mobile number.</li>
                    <li>In many cases simply your phone number, because it's unique and easy to remember.
                    </li>
                    <p>
                        The next time you wish to transact through the Site or trade a new product or service,
                        all you need to do is enter your Expressshow! registered Mobile number and password;
                        the system looks up the information it needs to assist you. In addition, if you
                        update the information associated with your Expressshow! registered Mobile number,
                        it will be available for all your transactions with Expressshow! globally.</p>
                </ol>
                <span class="title">When we Disclose your information:</span>
                <ol>
                    <li>Expressshow! takes your privacy very seriously. Be assured that Expressshow! does
                        not sell or rent your contact information to other marketers.</li>
                    <li>To help us to provide superior service, your personal information may be shared
                        with other Users of the Site, affiliates, agents and legal entities within the Expressshow!
                        group globally who will safeguard it in accordance with Expressshow! privacy policy.
                    </li>
                    <li>There are also times when it may be advantageous for Expressshow! to make certain
                        personal information about you available to companies that Expressshow! has a strategic
                        relationship with or that perform work for Expressshow! to provide products and services
                        to you on our behalf. </li>
                    <li>These companies may help us process information, extend credit, fulfill customer
                        orders, deliver products to you, manage and enhance customer data, provide customer
                        service, assess your interest in our products and services, or conduct customer
                        research or satisfaction surveys.</li>
                    <li>These companies are also obligated to protect your personal information in accordance
                        with Expressshow! policies.</li>
                    <li>Without such information being made available, it would be difficult for you to
                        trade/transact at Expressshow!, have products/services delivered to you, receive
                        customer service, provide us feedback to improve our products and services, or access
                        certain services, requests, and content on the Expressshow! website.</li>
                    <p>
                        At times we may be required by law or litigation to disclose your personal information.
                        We may also disclose information about you if we determine that for national security,
                        law enforcement, or other issues of public importance, disclosure is necessary.</p>
                </ol>
                <span class="title">How we protect your personal information:</span>
                <ol>
                    <li>Expressshow! takes precautions including administrative, technical, and physical
                        measures to safeguard your personal information against loss, theft, and misuse,
                        as well as unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.</li>
                    <li>You can help us by also taking precautions to protect your personal data when you
                        are on the Internet. Change your passwords often using a combination of letters
                        and numbers.</li>
                </ol>
                <span class="title">Integrity of your personal information:</span>
                <ol>
                    <li>Expressshow! has safeguards in place to keep your personal information accurate,
                        complete, and up to date for the purposes for which it is used. </li>
                    <li>Naturally, you always have the right to access and correct the personal information
                        you have provided.</li>
                    <li>You can help us ensure that your contact information and preferences are accurate
                        and complete. </li>
                    <li>And you can request a copy of your personal information, your trade/transaction
                        history, and your interactions with our customer service personnel by contacting
                        us.</li>
                </ol>
                <span class="title">Cookies and other technologies:</span>
                <ol>
                    <li>As is standard practice on many corporate websites, Expressshow! website uses "cookies"
                        and other technologies to help us to understand which parts of our websites are
                        the most popular, where our visitors are going, and how much time they spend there.</li>
                    <li>We use cookies to customize your experience and provide greater convenience each
                        time you interact with us. </li>
                    <li>We use cookies and other technologies to study traffic patterns on our website,
                        to make it even more rewarding as well as to study the effectiveness of our customer
                        communications.</li>
                </ol>
                <p>
                    For example, knowing your first name lets us welcome you with a greeting the next
                    time you visit the Site. If, however, you prefer not to have such information stored
                    on your computer, you may disable cookies on your computer as provided by your operating
                    system. Please note that certain features of the Expressshow! website will not be
                    available once cookies are disabled.</p>
                <p>
                    As is true of most Web sites, we gather certain information automatically and store
                    it in log files. This information includes internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser
                    type, internet service provider (ISP), referring/exit pages, operating system, date/time
                    stamp, and clickstream data.</p>
                <p>
                    We store all of this information in a secure database located in and outside of
                    India. We do not knowingly solicit personal information from minors or send them
                    requests for personal information. Expressshow! website has links to the sites of
                    other companies. Expressshow! is not responsible for their privacy practices. We
                    encourage you to learn about the privacy policies of those companies. Expressshow!
                    may update its privacy policy from time to time.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you do not want Expressshow! to communicate to you about the Expressshow! news,
                    updates and the latest information on products and services you may do so by editing
                    your profile from "My Account" section and update your personal contact information
                    and preferences accordingly on provision.</p>
